{"tid":1175180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［今次fatfat]有隻流浪貓屎忽撞棍，入咗個貓糧倉庫⋯⋯","createTime":"2019-05-28T11:28:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T12:14:33.000Z","uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"743352a2baaba23e5f1c348dbd007a4cdf6c67ef","tid":1175180,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T11:28:22.000Z","msg":"跟著變成咁￼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/05/28/192445_5cdc87016b966d4cde7d6d45a2947b81.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F28%2F192445_5cdc87016b966d4cde7d6d45a2947b81.png&h=59421f0d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/05/28/192446_afa056ea31ce6b24f00916389c7c9305.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F28%2F192446_afa056ea31ce6b24f00916389c7c9305.png&h=8a36ec1b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/05/28/192448_964358f7cdb6018a84698ac6e5de167e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F28%2F192448_964358f7cdb6018a84698ac6e5de167e.png&h=6bde704c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n⋯這張貓咪叫做 Hercules，在2007年被送到俄勒岡動物收容所，當時被送到收容所時，就因為胖胖的身軀受到關注，還因此登上多家媒體。 <br />\n<br />\nHercules之所以會這麼胖，全是因為牠在街頭流浪期間，發現了一個裝有滿滿貓糧的倉庫，於是貪吃的牠展開了「吃到飽」的快樂生活，結果吃著吃著，就這樣變成肉肉喵喵啦XD（看看牠跟旁邊那只貓的對比，體型根本已經寬出3倍以上啦） <br />\n<br />\n最後Hercules因為吃得太胖，導致牠卡在小門無法出去，才會因此被人發現，幸好在被送到動物收容所之後，牠很快就找到失散多年的主人，終於可以回到牠溫馨有愛的家中囉～ <br />\n<br />\n超胖浪浪貓咪的故事早在2007年就被媒體報導，但最近又再度引起大家討論，如今肥貓的報導影片也在YouTube創下690萬的點閱率，不過雖然牠胖胖的樣子很可愛，但是為了牠的健康著想，減肥還是很重要的阿！ <br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=6eLIMc4khe0&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6eLIMc4khe0%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=AW73mzr4JVDAANnbo7Up2AZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=14c98bc8\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=6eLIMc4khe0&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.damaxww.com/post953281\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.damaxww.com%2Fpost953281&d=AW73mzr4JVDAANnbo7Up2AZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=f0be937d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.damaxww.com/post953281</a>"},{"pid":"b0a52423dc79247e33cc1cc5247a23eabcec19e5","tid":1175180,"uid":30837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T11:49:42.000Z","msg":"肥撚到隻豹咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb2415e2085298d65caf7bbe4cdf12f262f4b7b3","tid":1175180,"uid":75050,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b0a52423dc79247e33cc1cc5247a23eabcec19e5","tid":1175180,"uid":30837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T11:49:42.000Z","msg":"肥撚到隻豹咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BO8Dbeu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBO8Dbeu.png&h=41eb6ec1&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}